parameters: \n<Davies>Thank you for working with us. We'll make
our way back to the castle on our own.
\n<Claire>They didn't help us out all that much...
\n<Davies>Come on, Claire. Give credit when it's due.
\n<Claire>You can go do whatever you want, but
the four of us are REAL adventurers. We're
going to get that tablet piece ourselves!
monsters messed up my partner real bad.
\solI guess you could say he's... out cold?
The Frozen Labyrinth is believed to have been built
by the same civilization that constructed the Lakeside
Labyrinth. However, this maze is a big step up.
With three floors, slippery ice all over the place,
guardian ice golems, and a host of powerful enemies,
the Frozen Labyrinth is very difficult to get through.
However, adventurers brave and strong enough to
explore the labyrinth will be rewarded with a
variety of enemy drops and assorted other loot.
Going further in unprepared may very well be the
end of you! Proceed with caution!
